a:17:{s:4:"name";s:6:"Liv 52";s:11:"small_descr";s:117:"Liv.52 is a double strength hepatospecific formulation, designed for the treatment and management of liver disorders.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:119:"Liv.52 ist ein starkes homöopathisches Mittel, das zur Behandlung und Linderung von Leberstörungen verwendet wird.   ";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:110:"Liv.52 est une formulation à double concentration hepatospecific, utilisé pour traiter les troubles du foie.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:143:"Liv.52 es una formulación de especificación hepática de doble fuerza , diseñada para el tratamiento y manejo de los trastornos del hígado.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:131:"Liv.52 è una formulazione ad azione epatica di doppia forza, progettata per il trattamento e la direzione dei disordini di fegato.";s:10:"full_descr";s:2133:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Liv.52 simply ensures optimum liver function. It helps regulate levels of enzymes and optimizes assimilation. Liv.52 has also been found to be associated with an increase in serum albumin, which is another indication of the liver protection it provides. Recent work shows that Liv.52 has a cholesterol-regulating action. Clinically, it helps maintain healthy levels of serum cholesterol, lipoproteins, phospholipids and triglycerides.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>Use Liv.52 as directed by your doctor. Check the label on the medicine for exact dosing instructions.</p><p>Take Liv.52 by mouth at least 30 minutes before or 2 hours after eating.</p><p>Do not eat grapefruit or drink grapefruit juice while you take Liv.52. <br />The effects of Liv.52 are not immediate. Although you may experience the benefits of Liv.52 2 to 4 weeks after beginning treatment, treatment for up to 12 weeks may be necessary before Liv.52 takes effect.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>Please consult your physician to prescribe the dosage that best suits your condition.</p><p>If you miss a dose of this medicine and you are using it regularly, take it as soon as possible. If you do not remember until later, skip the missed dose and go back to your regular dosing schedule. Do not take 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p><strong>MORE INFO:</strong></p><p>Active ingredient:&nbsp;Himsra (Capparis spinosa),&nbsp;Kasani (Cichorium intybus)</p><p>Other components:</p><p>Kakamachi (Solanum nigrum)	32mg<br /> Arjuna (Terminalia arjuna)	32mg<br /> Kasamarda (Cassia occidentalis)	 16mg<br /> Biranjasipha (Achillea millefolium)	16mg<br /> Jhavuka (Tamarix gallica)	16mg</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>There are no known contraindications.</p><p>Consult your healthcare professional if pregnant or nursing.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>As a powerful detoxifier, side effects may include:</p><p>nausea,</p><p>exhaustion and body aches.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:8:"24.19536";s:9:"pack_name";s:6:"bottle";s:4:"type";s:2:"ml";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:4:{i:200;a:5:{i:5534;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5534";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:200;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:5:"57.18";s:4:"name";s:6:"Liv 52";}i:5535;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5535";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:200;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"46.45875";s:4:"name";s:6:"Liv 52";}i:5536;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5536";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:200;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"42.885";s:4:"name";s:6:"Liv 52";}i:5537;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5537";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:200;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"41.09813";s:4:"name";s:6:"Liv 52";}i:5538;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5538";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:200;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"40.026";s:4:"name";s:6:"Liv 52";}}i:120;a:5:{i:5539;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5539";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6: